column2: SELECT s.SpecObjID,s.targetObjID,s.bestObjID,s.fluxObjID,s.class,s.subclass,s.survey,s.instrument,s.ra,s.dec,s.z,s.zErr,s.velDisp,s.velDispErr,   p.objID,p.mode,p.type,p.probPSF,p.ra,p.dec,p.fiberMag_r,p.fiberMagErr_r,p.deVAB_r,p.deVABErr_r,p.deVPhi_r,p.deVPhiErr_r,p.deVRad_r,p.deVRadErr_r,p.deVMag_r,p.deVMagErr_r,p.extinction_r,p.dered_r  FROM SpecObjAll as s,   PhotoObjAll as p WHERE   s.class=&&& and   s.sciencePrimary=# and   ((ra># and ra<# and dec># and dec<#) or      (ra># and ra<# and dec># and dec<#) or      (ra># and ra<# and dec># and dec<#) or      (ra># and ra<# and dec># and dec<#) or      (ra># and ra<# and dec># and dec<#)) and   s.bestObjID = p.objID    INTO mydb.newSDSSinGAMAmatchSpecPhoto
